#

Cottage Cheese and Avocado Toast

5 min
$3.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free Option

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

QuickHealthyBreakfastSnack

Description

A creamy and nutritious toast topped with rich avocado and protein-packed cottage cheese, perfect for a quick breakfast or snack.

Ingredients

  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • cottage cheese: 1/2 cup
  • avocado: 1 medium
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • red pepper flakes: optional, to taste
